description:
This pack features:
• Playable brawler Rocksteady
• Alternate Rocksteady costumes

Note:
Rocksteady and the content contained in this pack are also included in the Nickelodeon All-Star Brawl 2 Season Pass (sold separately).

In order to use this downloadable content, you will need Nickelodeon All-Star Brawl 2 (sold separately).
name: Nickelodeon All-Star Brawl 2 - Rocksteady Brawl Pack
